extension.workbenchStudio.backgrounds.ed:
Image list. Each entry is either a URL/path string, or an object `{ "background-image": "<url>", ...overrides }` for per-image CSS overrides. Example:
```
"images": [
  // simple string forms
  "https://hostname/online.jpg",
  "file:///local/path/img.jpeg",
  "/home/xie/images",
  // per-image overrides
  {
    "background-image": "file:///local/path/other.jpg",
    "opacity": "0.4",
    "background-size": "200px"
  }
]
```
